profile_positions.description:
Work experience at the end of my MSc.

The key duties have been:
- Managing the on road part and the relationship with 6 external suppliers;
- Responsible for the work of ~700 couriers in total at the Delivery Station;
- Monitoring and analysing the KPIs, researching the root cause of problems;
- Drawing up proposals for process improvement by gathering information on flows and data in order to contribute to the company's strategic plans.

Accomplishments:
- Driver HERO: voted by the logistics companies as Driver HERO (Helpful, Engaged, Respectful, Obsessed) of the month.
- Sustainability Ambassadors: I was responsible for developing environmental sustainability initiatives, such as recycling of DPI, creation of weekly information content called "Pills of Sustainability", recycling of EPAL pallets, improvement of the green areas. The aim was to involve associates and managers in order to raise awareness and contribute to a greener workplace.

Summer internship undertaken by personal initiative.

Work activities in the SAP Finance consultancy field by:
- Following the business requirements part of the client for a roll out project of sap FI on all the Countries;
- Managing the configuration part of the module FI to manage the business processes in the new ERP;
- Testing all the transactions for assets and fiscal documents.

Internship carried out during the studies.

The main tasks have been:
- Analysis of company flows and their adaptation to internal and external constraints, guaranteeing the coherence of the systems and compliance with the requirements of the reference ISO standards;
- Constant updating of the documentation necessary for the analysis and performance of the Management Systems;
- Staff training and information on the management tools of the systems adopted by the Organisation;
- Planning and management of inspection visits and consequent collection of documents.

Accomplishments:
- I proposed a solution in order to reduce the number of causes of defects during the production process, it has involved ~150 persons.
- Thanks to the work carried out, the company was able to obtain ISO 9001:2015 for Quality, certification issued by the Bureau Veritas;
- I wrote my Bachelor Degree thesis: " Quality within the company: the case of Vibram SPA" with a focus part regarding the ISO 9001:2015 certification.
